Oh Baby Games has been quiet about what it has been working on, but has released teasers of the game leading up to this announcement. Tran <a href="https://twitter.com/passytee/status/1605167902319325184?s=20&amp;t=fdcPXwOfUWZx4HNBi3D0Og" data-v-f87c67ca="">tweeted</a> a trailer video in December of its first game.&nbsp;<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
The Oh Baby Games team <a href="https://ohbabygames.com/news" data-v-f87c67ca="">said</a> it has worked on games such as the Call of Duty franchise, League of Legends, and Magic: The Gathering.&nbsp;
